---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<Layout title="资料页面">
  <main>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">首页</a>
      <a href="/about/">资料领取</a>
    </nav>

    <Card
      <img src="/a07c3d350788d5c4da628c36c36dbe2.jpg" alt="微信二维码" />
      <div class="instructions">
        <h2>领取流程说明</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>扫描二维码添加微信好友。</li>
          <li>发送消息“领取资料”。</li>
          <li>等待回复，获取资料链接。</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </Card>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    width: 70%; 
    max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
    color: rgb(112, 142, 207);
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    background-image: url('https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/orj360/007edkYwgy1hrbw4ptuzvj32c03401ky.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }
  nav {
    position: fixed; /* 固定导航条在页面顶部 */
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(193, 247, 203, 0.8); 
    z-index: 50; 
  }
  nav a {
    color: #ffffff;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 1rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .astro-a {
    position: absolute;
    top: -32px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translatex(-50%);
    width: 220px;
    height: 550px;
    z-index: -1;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }
  h2 {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .text-gradient {
    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-size: 400%;
    background-position: 0%;
  }
  .instructions {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #000000; 
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .instructions code {
    font-size: 3em;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #000000; 
  }
  .instructions ol {
    font-size: 1.2em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #000000; 
  }
</style>